metadata.name: Gosh It Good
metadata.description:
AI series exploring thoughts about AI art from an artists perspective.

AI artwork and digital painting.

Comes with Gallery Quality Print.
Shipping & packaging included.

Print only guaranteed for the first buyer to claim print.

Printed with Canon Pro 1000 with original inks.
On Hahnemühle FineArt Pearl 285 gsm paper.
Size 594x420mm. 20mm border.
Signed and numbered edition 1 of 1.
